        >chech pointing is that the secondary namenode combines the edit log and fsimage and update it in fsimage
        >so that every operations on hdfs is monitored.
        >this is done periodically for every hour or it can be configured to a certain time
        >thus the updated fsimage has entire information about the operation on file system
